@ryerye11 
Mounting is a term when you use a program like Daemon Tools Lite to mount a disc image like the one you will get in this torrent as a normal disc. Then, it acts pretty much as if you inserted a real disc, letting you install it and everything.
I gotta say though, if you don't know what mounting is you should probably read up a bit more before trying to install this kind of program. It can get really confusing, even to those with experience.
